These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, lilac, yellow, apricot
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, american, canadian
 1. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the person who likes lavender##8
 2. the argentine is not to the left of the argentine##8
 3. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes lavender is not to the left of the person who likes apricot##8
 5. the argentine is not to the right of the argentine##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the australian and the person who likes lilac##2
 9. the canadian is the person watching family movies##1
10. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the canadian##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the american##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who likes lilac##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Color         | lilac  | yellow  | apricot  | lavender |
| Nationality     | argentine    | american | australian     | canadian    |

