.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing, baking, gardening
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, baseball, biathlon
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is between the owner of the dog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
13. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
15. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby      | card-games | baking | gardening  | rock-climbing  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | baseball  | biathlon | cricket |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

