The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, firefighter, engineer, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, folk, jazz
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
 3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
 4. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the paramedic##8
 6. the person traveling to rome is not to the left of the engineer##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the engineer is on the left of the videographer##1
 9. the videographer is on the left of the firefighter##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the paramedic is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the videographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| City         | nizza    | rome   | paris | edinburgh |
| Job   | paramedic     | engineer  | videographer   | firefighter      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | folk      | jazz       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

