 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 5. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the person eating kale##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the montecristo-smoker##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 8. the person eating peach is the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the person eating lime is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the montecristo-smoker##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the bolivar-smoker##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the person eating peach is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
