.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, january, july
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, thriller, adventure, romance
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching romance movies##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Birthday   | april  | july      | january     | march     |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | adventure  | romance     | thriller  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

